operation.documentation:
[THIS METHOD IS DEPRECATED] Synchronize User. Parameters: nmdomainuid->Unique user identifier on Domain Controller
                                        ID->Identifier for the User; Name->The user's name;
                                        Login->The user's login;
                                        Email->Email address for this user;
                                        Fglanguage->Default languge of this user
                                        Fguserenabled->User enabled
                                        Fguserblocked->User blocked
                                        Fgnotice->Enviar email
                                        Idarea->User department;
                                        nmarea->User department name;
                                        Idposition->User position
                                        nmposition->User position name
                                        nmdefsynchfilter->First time synch field
                                        oidconnection->Connection identifier
                                        cdleader->Leader id
                                        Return values: SUCCESS->Primary key value for the user(CDUSER); FAILURE:-1.
